data.description: Hidden Gem close to downtown!Upgraded home lots of square footage! Motivated seller! Unbelievable Value! This Exquisite Home is an Entertainer's Dream! Nestled near downtown and in front of the new film school by the rail yards. Every detail of this home is designed to perfection, boasting 5 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a spacious bonus/family room not to mention natural light from the skylights. Upon entering, you'll be enchanted by the stunning floors that seamlessly complement the high ceilings, creating a bright and open atmosphere. This remarkable property boasts numerous outstanding features, including walk in closets and 2 furnaces and 2 ac units. Act now and make this dream home your own!
